<hr size=1> I have Geforce 2 GTS's on both my computers, and at least on the slower one I noticed a BIG difference in the speed and overall smoothness. This is great, however I noticed two things sort of buggy.<br>
<br>
1. The font size of all the text is too large, not just the chat font size (which is customizable) but all test. Sort of annoying because it runs past the windows/buttons.<br>
<br>
2. Seems like randomly the lines of the different windows appear in the wrong positions at times. The windows are still there, but then these other black lines appear.<br>
<br>
Anyone else getting these two things? I figure the text thing is probably affecting everyone but not sure about the second..maybe I should email them about it.<br>
